OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1776280294
OL,3,CUlster University to cut around 450
OL,4,Cjobs
OL,6,FUlster University is to make around
OL,7,F450 staff redundant.
OL,9,FStaff were made aware of the job cuts
OL,10,Fat a virtual meeting with the vice-
OL,11,Fchancellor Professor Paul Bartholomew,
OL,12,Fon Wednesday.
OL,14,FIt is understood the university is
OL,15,Frequired to make savings of #25
OL,16,Fmillion.
OL,18,FUlster University has more than 30,000
OL,19,Fstudents and employs 3,100 staff.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
