FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1776280294
OL,3,CUlster University to cut around 450
OL,4,Cjobs
OL,6,FThe university has campuses in
OL,7,FBelfast, Londonderry and Coleraine as
OL,8,Fwell a specialised sports village in
OL,9,FJordanstown.
OL,11,FIt is unclear at this stage which
OL,12,Fcampuses will be affected.
OL,14,FIn a statement to UTV, a university
OL,15,Fspokesperson said: "Redundancies
OL,16,Facross the Higher Education Sector
OL,17,Fhave become unavoidable.
OL,19,F"To date, more than 100 institutions
OL,20,Facross the UK have downsized their
OL,21,Fstaffing complement.
OL,26,@wD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1776280294
OL,3,CUlster University to cut around 450
OL,4,Cjobs
OL,6,F"Ulster University has sought to hold
OL,7,Foff on making redundancies while
OL,8,Fcontinuing to work with the Department
OL,9,Ffor the Economy, through their
OL,10,Freviews, on possible changes to the HE
OL,11,Ffunding model in Northern Ireland.
OL,13,F"It has recently been made clear to us
OL,14,Fthat a sustainable funding model is
OL,15,Fnot going to be forthcoming, and
OL,16,Fregretfully we must now act to reduce
OL,17,Four costs."
OL,26,@yD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1776280294
OL,3,CUlster University to cut around 450
OL,4,Cjobs
OL,6,FNorman Hagan, chair of the Ulster
OL,7,FUniversity branch of the University
OL,8,Fand College Union (UCU) said the job
OL,9,Fcuts were "deeply alarming and
OL,10,Funsustainable" and that compulsory
OL,11,Fredundancies would be "strongly
OL,12,Fresisted".
OL,14,FMr Hagan said staff were "ready to
OL,15,Fengage", but would not "stand idly by
OL,16,Fand let our university flounder
OL,17,Fthrough government or university
OL,18,Fneglect".
OL,26,@qD@KOUrD@NO]sD@WOUtD@IO]vD@ZOUwD@GO]wD@
OL,26,AXOUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1776280294
OL,3,CUlster University to cut around 450
OL,4,Cjobs
OL,6,F"Staff already work under sustained
OL,7,Fpressure, with rising workloads and
OL,8,Fimpossible demands. Imposing
OL,9,Fredundancies on this scale is deeply
OL,10,Falarming and unsustainable," he said.
OL,12,F"Removing hundreds of staff will
OL,13,Ffundamentally damage the student
OL,14,Fexperience and weaken academic
OL,15,Fprovision."
OL,17,FHe added: "We are also clear:
OL,18,Fcompulsory redundancies will be
OL,19,Fstrongly resisted.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@\O]tD@AOUwD@KO]yD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1776280294
OL,3,CUlster University to cut around 450
OL,4,Cjobs
OL,6,F"This is not just about jobs, it is
OL,7,Fabout protecting the integrity of
OL,8,Fhigher education in Northern Ireland.
OL,10,F"Ulster University plays a critical
OL,11,Fcivic role, and decisions of this
OL,12,Fmagnitude if forced through would have
OL,13,Ffar-reaching detrimental consequences
OL,14,Ffor students, local communities, and
OL,15,Fthe wider regional economy."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
