OL,3,CUlster University to cut around 450
OL,4,Cjobs
OL,6,FMr Hagan said: "You cannot cut your
OL,7,Fway to excellence, removing 450 jobs
OL,8,Frisks hollowing out the very
OL,9,Ffoundations that make this university
OL,10,Fviable, credible, and capable of
OL,11,Fserving its students and the broader
OL,12,Fsociety."
